 about treatment of netblocks.
Netblock filtering in ORBS is optional. This is something else people seem
to be forgetting. The returned A record is different for each type so you
can choose to filter them. Some mailers unfortunately don't support this
feature (eg exim).  127.0.0.4 is the return for a netblk filter.
